but think about it carefully.

295
00:20:49,690 --> 00:20:50,790
Don't you find it strange?

296
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:52,610
My father and I came back this time

297
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:54,120
for Yanqiu's marriage.

298
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:55,720
But as soon as he came back,

299
00:20:55,740 --> 00:20:57,260
he rented a mansion outside,

300
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,080
and he didn't come back often.

301
00:20:59,370 --> 00:21:00,090
as if he was

302
00:21:00,110 --> 00:21:00,960
hiding from something.

303
