Uncle Yingheng asked me to rent that mansion for him.

304
00:21:04,230 --> 00:21:05,800
He said it was to organize manuscripts peacefully,

305
00:21:06,210 --> 00:21:07,410
not to avoid anyone.

306
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:10,330
The weather and the life

307
00:21:10,790 --> 00:21:11,790
are both unpredictable.

308
00:21:12,650 --> 00:21:13,170
Banxia.

309
00:21:13,740 --> 00:21:14,980
I know it's hard for you to accept

310
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:15,870
Uncle Yingheng's death right now.

311
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,350
But now that it's come to this,

312
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:18,440
you must stay strong.

313
00:21:21,310 --> 00:21:22,400
Tingzhou, the mirror.

314
00:21:25,060 --> 00:21:26,130
I found this mirror

315
00:21:26,160 --> 00:21:27,490
in my father's room.

316
00:21:27,840 --> 00:21:28,970
It can only reflect objects,

317
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:29,930
not people.

318
00:21:30,330 --> 00:21:31,280
I went to the fire scene

319
00:21:31,300 --> 00:21:32,020
at Penglai Alley

320
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:33,080
and found a mirror

321
00:21:33,110 --> 00:21:34,030
which is exactly the same as this one.

322
00:21:34,510 --> 00:21:35,830
Isn't this suspicious enough?

323
00:21:36,940 --> 00:21:37,340
This...

324
00:21:47,480 --> 00:21:48,280
How could this be?

325
00:21:49,030 --> 00:21:49,750
No way.

326
00:21:50,330 --> 00:21:50,890
It clearly couldn't

327
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:51,990
reflect anything yesterday.

328
00:21:52,240 --> 00:21:53,480
Tingzhou, you saw it too, right?

329
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:55,330
Yes.

330
00:21:55,550 --> 00:21:56,480
I saw it too.

331
00:21:57,340 --> 00:21:58,470
It couldn't reflect people.

332
00:22:02,480 --> 00:22:03,110
I know.

333
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:07,160
It must have been a powerful demon

334
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:08,640
