335
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:10,000
That's why we couldn't see it.

336
00:22:11,070 --> 00:22:12,310
I know a demon hunter.

337
00:22:12,720 --> 00:22:13,510
-We can…
-Banxia!

338
00:22:17,720 --> 00:22:18,240
Tingzhou.

339
00:22:18,850 --> 00:22:19,810
Help your lady back to her room.

340
00:22:25,640 --> 00:22:26,270
Why?

341
00:22:31,180 --> 00:22:31,990
Why can't you

342
00:22:32,020 --> 00:22:33,630
