345
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:43,480
I'm not sick!

346
00:22:44,440 --> 00:22:46,160
I said my father is still alive!

347
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:47,800
These are all caused by demons!

348
00:22:47,830 --> 00:22:48,350
Demons?

349
00:22:49,110 --> 00:22:49,920
