363
00:23:16,790 --> 00:23:17,790
She approached you just to...

364
00:23:17,810 --> 00:23:18,650
Shut up!

365
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:35,030
Sir, welcome.

366
00:23:36,080 --> 00:23:37,000
Sir, welcome.

367
00:23:37,000 --> 00:23:37,750
Please, come in.

368
00:23:38,790 --> 00:23:39,870
Mr. Zhang.

369
00:23:41,680 --> 00:23:42,920
Sir, please come inside.

370
00:23:43,350 --> 00:23:43,790
Please, come in.

371
00:23:44,070 --> 00:23:45,550
This is your first time here, right, Sir?

372
00:23:46,350 --> 00:23:46,910
Please, come in.

373
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:55,640
Come on. This way.

374
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:57,160
Have another drink.

375
00:23:58,510 --> 00:23:59,640
Is this your first time here?

376
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:24,440
Where did you come from, you brute?

377
00:24:31,010 --> 00:24:31,930
How dare you hit me?

378
00:24:35,080 --> 00:24:35,720
Mr. Song.

379
00:24:35,920 --> 00:24:36,440
Mr. Song!

380
00:24:37,160 --> 00:24:38,290
Why are you leaving?

381
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:41,110
Sir,

382
00:24:42,110 --> 00:24:42,590
Chuntao

383
00:24:42,880 --> 00:24:44,550
