384
00:24:44,820 --> 00:24:45,230
How about

385
00:24:45,310 --> 00:24:46,480
I arrange some other girl

386
00:24:46,510 --> 00:24:46,960
for you?

387
00:24:50,630 --> 00:24:51,740
I won't disturb you any further.

388
00:24:51,900 --> 00:24:52,310
Chuntao.

389
00:24:52,620 --> 00:24:53,470
Take good care of this gentleman here.

390
00:25:11,000 --> 00:25:11,480
Sir.

391
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:13,640
Your bamboo hat...

392
00:25:14,170 --> 00:25:15,540
