400
00:26:01,730 --> 00:26:03,250
Of course I believe you, My Lady.

401
00:26:04,280 --> 00:26:05,390
But what's the use

402
00:26:05,410 --> 00:26:05,940
of me being the only one

403
00:26:05,970 --> 00:26:06,770
