408
00:26:22,510 --> 00:26:23,070
No.

409
00:26:23,550 --> 00:26:24,780
He must be nearby.

410
00:26:25,030 --> 00:26:25,510
Why?

411
00:26:26,930 --> 00:26:28,340
Sound eels are different from other demons.

412
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:30,270
For him, beautiful sounds

413
00:26:30,270 --> 00:26:31,110
are both food

414
00:26:31,160 --> 00:26:32,110
and medicine.

415
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:33,440
Since he's injured,

416
00:26:33,720 --> 00:26:34,640
he'll definitely search for

417
00:26:34,640 --> 00:26:35,760
beautiful sounds in the city

418
00:26:35,790 --> 00:26:36,720
to heal himself.

419
00:26:45,330 --> 00:26:46,610
He just won't leave us alone.

420
00:27:11,030 --> 00:27:12,030
What should we do?

421
00:27:14,010 --> 00:27:15,250
She's been playing the whole night.

422
00:27:15,740 --> 00:27:16,740
