426
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:21,640
Right.

427
00:27:21,660 --> 00:27:22,100
Right.

428
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:23,830
Madame, it's a matter of life and death.

429
00:27:24,030 --> 00:27:25,000
It's a matter of life and death, Madame.

430
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:25,510
Right.

431
00:27:26,240 --> 00:27:26,680
Alright.

432
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:28,270
Let's report this to the government.

433
00:27:29,810 --> 00:27:30,300
Qiusheng!

434
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:31,400
Come here.

435
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:33,240
Come on.

436
00:27:33,630 --> 00:27:34,480
You're the fastest.

437
00:27:34,750 --> 00:27:35,340
Go to the government office

438
00:27:35,550 --> 00:27:36,320
and ask Chief Constable Song

439
00:27:36,350 --> 00:27:37,510
to bring enough people over.

440
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:38,300
Go quickly.

441
00:27:38,540 --> 00:27:39,060
Yes.

442
00:27:44,620 --> 00:27:45,970
Why are you so flustered?

443
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:48,550
Do you know Chief Constable Song?

444
00:27:48,570 --> 00:27:49,110
Yes, I do.

445
00:27:49,310 --> 00:27:50,550
Come with me and report to the government.

446
00:27:51,240 --> 00:27:51,790
Report to the government?

447
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:53,490
Let's go. Someone is causing trouble.

448
00:28:06,030 --> 00:28:06,880
May I ask who you are...

449
00:28:25,310 --> 00:28:26,720
Quite the refined entertainment, isn't it?

450
00:28:27,550 --> 00:28:30,000
If she keeps playing, she'll bleed out.

451
00:28:31,750 --> 00:28:32,520
Young lady?

452
00:28:42,360 --> 00:28:43,210
You've woken up?

453
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:46,350
Wearing a bamboo hat indoors,

454
00:28:46,930 --> 00:28:47,720
don't you feel stifled?

455
00:28:49,350 --> 00:28:50,110
Run while you still can.

456
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,200
You're really getting uglier and uglier.

457
00:30:45,550 --> 00:30:46,180
Chi Xue.

458
00:30:46,590 --> 00:30:47,160
Take it away.

459
00:31:12,140 --> 00:31:13,540
I received a letter from your fiancé.

460
00:31:15,070 --> 00:31:16,290
He knows what happened to your father.

461
00:31:16,720 --> 00:31:18,020
He said he'd come to Nanyang

462
00:31:18,550 --> 00:31:19,400
as soon as he finishes his work.

463
00:31:22,310 --> 00:31:23,030
I've inquired about him.

464
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:24,560
He's a good guy.

465
00:31:24,920 --> 00:31:25,830
Pretty talented.

466
00:31:26,830 --> 00:31:27,880
Uncle Yingheng had good taste.

467
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:35,240
Banxia.

468
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:37,790
I've got news about Manniang.

469
00:31:41,510 --> 00:31:42,400
Do you still remember

470
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,410
that throat-slitting scoundrel

471
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,640
