478
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:01,590
Of course I don't believe it.

479
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:04,270
She's just a weak woman.

480
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:12,680
I'll continue to investigate.

481
00:32:14,130 --> 00:32:15,360
But regardless,

482
00:32:15,850 --> 00:32:16,760
there are no demons in this world,

483
00:32:16,790 --> 00:32:17,750
and that's a fact.

484
00:32:21,050 --> 00:32:21,400
So,

485
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:22,550
you should stop overthinking it.

486
00:32:24,110 --> 00:32:24,830
Now,

487
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:26,510
although Uncle Yingheng is gone,

488
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:29,110
we will take good care of you.

489
00:32:32,810 --> 00:32:33,590
I understand.

490
00:32:38,030 --> 00:32:38,790
It's raining.

491
00:32:39,060 --> 00:32:39,740
Let me walk you back.

492
00:32:40,490 --> 00:32:41,000
No need.

493
00:32:42,470 --> 00:32:43,780
I can go back by myself.

494
00:32:45,920 --> 00:32:47,520
Go back and rest early.

495
00:33:13,740 --> 00:33:14,460
My Lady.

496
00:33:14,700 --> 00:33:15,830
I've finished packing.

497
00:33:16,850 --> 00:33:17,370
Okay.

498
00:33:27,540 --> 00:33:28,020
Let's go.

499
00:33:34,910 --> 00:33:37,470
[To Yanqiu]

500
00:33:43,610 --> 00:33:44,370
It's raining so heavily.

501
00:33:47,600 --> 00:33:48,230
Mister.

502
00:33:48,820 --> 00:33:50,300
Is there a ferry dock ahead

503
00:33:50,570 --> 00:33:51,850
