506
00:33:54,100 --> 00:33:54,860
Every day at noon.

507
00:33:56,530 --> 00:33:57,600
Are you taking a boat to Guangping?

508
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:01,790
The boat only comes once a day.

509
00:34:02,600 --> 00:34:03,340
It's raining so heavily.

510
00:34:03,840 --> 00:34:05,010
I'm afraid you won't make it today.

511
00:34:05,030 --> 00:34:05,670
Wait until tomorrow.

512
00:34:08,219 --> 00:34:09,030
My Lady.

513
00:34:10,370 --> 00:34:11,969
How about we go back?

514
00:34:14,639 --> 00:34:15,800
