532
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:24,160
I killed the Human-faced Owl.

533
00:35:24,570 --> 00:35:25,990
Of course he wants to avenge his master

534
00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:27,610
by staying close to his enemy

535
00:35:27,640 --> 00:35:28,420
and waiting for the right time.

536
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,010
This sound eel

537
00:35:31,160 --> 00:35:32,120
is actually quite loyal.

538
00:35:37,180 --> 00:35:37,990
Keep a close eye on it.

539
00:36:01,970 --> 00:36:04,850
♫A familiar figure♫

