00:36:05,330 --> 00:36:08,440
♫Becomes clear in the haze♫

541
00:36:08,970 --> 00:36:13,400
♫Yet it's out of reach♫

542
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:18,790
♫Your earnest reminders♫

543
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:22,150
♫And words of concern♫

544
00:36:20,600 --> 00:36:21,450
Xuanye, you're back.

545
00:36:22,280 --> 00:36:23,280
