549
00:36:26,120 --> 00:36:26,640
It's okay.

550
00:36:26,800 --> 00:36:27,680
There will be a next time.

551
00:36:29,790 --> 00:36:32,810
♫Traces of bond♫

552
00:36:29,850 --> 00:36:31,280
