553
00:36:33,290 --> 00:36:36,300
♫With a sigh, we bid farewell♫

554
00:36:36,770 --> 00:36:42,300
♫Keeping you company, and seeing you off on a long journey♫

555
00:36:37,050 --> 00:36:38,050
