560
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:46,600
♫You're the same as before♫

561
00:36:47,080 --> 00:36:50,550
♫And I'm still following closely behind♫

562
00:36:47,370 --> 00:36:47,930
Xuanye.

563
00:36:49,450 --> 00:36:50,290
Now I finally know

564
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:51,090
