565
00:36:50,720 --> 00:36:56,310
♫Remember it day and night♫

566
00:36:51,680 --> 00:36:52,830
They like to eat lamb lung soup.

567
00:36:53,320 --> 00:36:54,820
Don't put any oil, salt, sauce or vinegar in it.

568
00:36:54,850 --> 00:36:55,900
Just boil it in plain water

569
00:36:55,970 --> 00:36:56,900
